---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - TaxPortal" description="TaxPortal privacy policy outlining our commitment to protecting your data and privacy.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-canvas dark:bg-primary">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-6 text-body dark:text-muted">
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> July 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>TaxPortal ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit and use our tax calculators, guides, and tools.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>TaxPortal calculators operate entirely in your browser. We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal or financial data entered into our calculators. All calculations are performed locally on your device.</p>
        <p>We may collect anonymized usage data to improve our services. This data does not contain personally identifiable information.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Since we do not collect personal data, there is no use of personal information beyond the anonymized analytics that help us improve the website experience.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>All calculations are performed in-browser. No user data is stored on our servers. No financial or personal information is stored, transmitted, or shared with any third party.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>TaxPortal uses minimal cookies for language preference and theme (light/dark mode) settings only. These cookies do not track or store any personal or financial information.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">6. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites or government tax authority pages. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those external sites.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>TaxPortal is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect data from anyone under 13.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@taxportal.com.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>